            <abstract>
                <p>Explications to the Gǝʿǝz <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3171Commen">Commentary on 
                    the Epistle to the Hebrews by John Chrysostom</ref> dictated by <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14363WaldaRufael">ʾalaqā Walda Rufāʾel of Goǧǧām</persName> 
                    at <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC6373Yawes">Yawǝš</placeName>, upon the order of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4779GossuZa">Goššu Zawde</persName>. According to A. d'Abbadie, 
                    a copy was made from the <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4779GossuZa">Goššu's</persName> own manuscript.</p>
